548
00:34:47.544 --> 00:34:49.545
Even if it did.
they'd still have to find us.

549
00:34:52.883 --> 00:34:54.842
I'm so sorry.
I never should have--

550
00:34:54.843 --> 00:34:56.010
No. no. no. no. no. no. no.

551
00:34:56.011 --> 00:34:57.386
